protected_spaces_details.description: Provision for children and young people

description: Redevelopment of site comprising the demolition of 189 existing residential units (including Heron Court, Robin Court, Sandpiper Court, Nightingale Court, Martin Court, Grebe Court and Kingfisher Court) and the construction of 3 blocks between 3 and 14 storeys to provide 399 residential units (containing 119 x 1 bed, 190 x 2 bed, 60 x 3 bed and 30 x 4 bed), together with 103sq.m (GIA) office / community facility (Use Class D1), semi-basement and ground floor car parking, cycle parking, landscaped public open space, private amenity space and other associated works.
